Title: S06E12 - nanoFramework: Unleashing the Power of C# in Embedded Systems and IoT with José Simões
Description: José Simões explores the .NET nanoFramework, a powerful platform for embedded systems and IoT development. Discover how this stripped-down version of the .NET Framework empowers developers to create applications for resource-constrained devices, while abstracting away the complexities of working with microcontrollers. Gain insights on the platform's unique features, such as productivity enhancements, code reusability, and seamless migration. Whether you're a seasoned developer or just starting out in the world of embedded systems, this podcast offers valuable insights and inspiration for leveraging the .NET nanoFramework in your projects
